commit.message: Update README with cmake instructions.
btorsim: Ignore outputs.
Move.
btorsim: Add support for more operators.
Add missing copyright headers.

btorsim: Allow state assignments for k > 0.

If a state does not have a next function, the witness must contain the
assignment in each time frame since the state is essentially an input.
btor2aiger: Do not translate BTOR outputs.
btor2aiger: Fix handling of states without next functions.
btor2aiger: Add missing calls to AIGER library.
btor2aiger: Fix adding outputs.
btor2aiger: Add option to ignore AIGER errors.
btor2aiger: Abort if file cannot be opened.
Add btorsplit to split multi-property files into single-property files.
Add script to setup all dependencies.
cmake: Add more options. Refactor configure script.
Add initial version of BTOR2 to AIGER bitblaster.

Remove udivo from README (#3)

Signed-off-by: Makai Mann <makaim@stanford.edu>
examples: Fix ne/neq.
btor2parser: Fix parsing ne/neq.
btor2parser: Allow symbols for const* tags.
btor2parser: Output tag does not require a sort id.
